snippet.title: Verisim Skies - Official Trailer (April 24th, 2023)
snippet.description:
Verisim Skies is a Vertical Shoot 'Em Up with an emphasis on story and cinematic action. Go forth, Champion. Find your purpose. Fulfill your destiny. Accept your fate.

Available now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2358970/Verisim_Skies/

Trailer Music: Makai Symphony - Battle Troopers
